    "title": "ファンレター",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "テイエムオペラオーにファンレターが届いた。",
            "enText": "A fan letter was sent to TM Operao.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -5106188456344787892
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": 2084652303979611759
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1909837787566116124,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "これは素晴らしい！！",
            "enText": "This is fantastic!!!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 58,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -5625593552021406033
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -1385347602316679320
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1851267956937427058,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "見てくれたまえ、トレーナー君！\n敬虔なファンが似顔絵を描いてくれたんだ！",
            "enText": "Look at that, Ms. Trainer! A devout fan drew \na portrait of you!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 4469271763537713810
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 5776886265248037225
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 936096779219638888
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6029641567920070378,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そう言って彼女が見せてくれたのは、\n子どもがクレヨンで描いたと\n思われる絵だった。",
            "enText": "She showed me a picture that appeared to have \nbeen drawn by a child with a crayon.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 35,
                    "pathId": 8125621555291896927
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 39,
                    "pathId": 7949068947175672973
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -8962662829425556539
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8533649680294666641,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "耳と尻尾を生やした……棒状の\nテイエムオペラオーらしき絵の周りは\n藍色のクレヨンで塗りつぶされている。",
            "enText": "Around a drawing that looks like a…… stick \nfigure of Taymu Operao with ears and tail. \npainted with indigo crayon.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "pathId": -4926441090763133767,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "すらりと伸びた体躯、思わず見惚れてしまう\nチャーミングな耳と尻尾――",
            "enText": "The sleek, elongated physique, the charming \nears and tail that you can't help but admire…",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": -5345616434698237964
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 127,
                    "pathId": -2849553897035938053
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 128,
                    "pathId": -1913024202966907794
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4101857538834540918,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "ボクの魅力をここまで忠実に再現するなんて、\n世の中にはとんでもない鬼才がいたものだ！",
            "enText": "There are some geniuses out there who have \nmanaged to recreate my charm so faithfully!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": 6120469475464908093
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 85,
                    "pathId": 4592692667579060020
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 6653782920956588070
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6248048937063615078,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "それに……ふむ、なるほど。\nこの藍色で表現しているのは宇宙か。",
            "enText": "And…… Hmmm, I see. Is it the universe that is \nrepresented by this indigo color?",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 42,
                    "pathId": -7153424329636979124
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -2233951674976364352
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5834183017598481529,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "いいね、ボクが銀河を駆ける姿！\nこの子のセンスは最高だ！",
            "enText": "I love it, the way I run across the galaxy! \nThis kid's got great taste!",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": 274211025009645931
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": -7232104171650904415
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3865315447517735987,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "ではボクもそのリクエストに応えなくてはね！",
            "enText": "Well, I'll have to respond to that request!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "えっ？",
                    "enText": "What?",
                    "nextBlock": 11
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 68,
                    "pathId": -8316596597846116308
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -9025286240478386783
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6916430716252890116,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "トレーナー君、宇宙で走るために\n有効なトレーニングはあるかい！？",
            "enText": "Trainer, do you have any effective training \nfor running in space?",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "本気で言ってる！？",
                    "enText": "I'm serious!",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": -2180356979135957469
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -5876763858646858768
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2763845172174707755,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "ああ、ボクはいつだって本気さ。",
            "enText": "Yeah, I'm always serious.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": -7947551173870194861
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": -2691904382746494534
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6117973082131393363,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "期待があるなら応じるまで。\n何事もやってみないとわからないだろう？",
            "enText": "If there is an expectation, we \nwill meet it. You never know until \nyou try everything, right?",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "けど宇宙か……",
                    "enText": "But space or ……",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 2236598528917304240
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": -9094820374623727289
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8162155110141623600,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……とりあえず宇宙飛行士の訓練の中から、\nトレセン学園でも行える内容を伝えてみた。",
            "enText": "…… In the meantime, I told them about some of \nthe training astronauts receive that can be \ndone at Thoresen Academy.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": 7843264281434163169
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": 5658796348807567445
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8185405730387681563,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "おや、いつも通りのメニューじゃ……。",
            "enText": "Oh, it's the same menu as usual. ……",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": 1171134872015926962
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": 3869993748784534571
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2274559254814433175,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "……はっ！？　待てよ！？\nそれじゃあつまり――",
            "enText": "…… Ha! Wait! So you're saying―",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 75,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 6339783053782147759
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 86,
                    "pathId": 4197920399241816459
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5399770629414673930,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "ボクは無意識のうちに、\n宇宙で頂点を取る特訓を実践していたのか！？",
            "enText": "Was I unconsciously practicing my training to \nreach the top of the universe?",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 51,
                    "pathId": -2539344280174607792
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 6717662261440733973
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3000500417235381004,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "はーっはっはっは！！\nさすがはボク、僅かな抜かりもないな！",
            "enText": "Ha-ha-ha-ha! That's my girl, not the \nslightest bit of flaws!",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": 9142464847249354359
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 6562477400683631524
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 646709446535011797,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "TM Opera O",
            "jpText": "では歩もうか、宇宙への1歩を。\n少女の望みを叶えるためにも！",
            "enText": "Let's walk, then, one step into space. And to \nmake a little girl's wish come true!",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 68,
                    "pathId": 2192391507879999665
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 6149975538245671993
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8522473881331853087,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "テイエムオペラオーはいつものように\n揺るぎない瞳で宣言したのだった。",
            "enText": "As always, TM Operao proclaimed \nwith eyes unwavering.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": 1285889291944229877
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": -2612154748426239019
                }
            ],
